OL,3,CBorder politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'friend and inspiration' Alex Salmond
OL,6,FPoliticians and former colleagues from
OL,7,Facross the political spectrum have
OL,8,Fbeen paying tribute to Alex Salmond
OL,9,Fwho died yesterday.
OL,11,FThe former First Minister of Scotland
OL,12,Fdied suddenly while at a conference in
OL,13,FNorth Macedonia yesterday (12 October).
OL,15,FHe was an influential and often
OL,16,Fcontroversial figure in Scottish and
OL,17,FUK politics, having led the Scottish
OL,18,FNational Party (SNP) to power in 2007
OL,19,Fand securing a referendum on Scottish
OL,20,Findependence in 2014.
