OL,3,CBorder politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'friend and inspiration' Alex Salmond
OL,6,FThe referendum resulted in 45% of
OL,7,Fvoters opting for Scotland to separate
OL,8,Ffrom the United Kingdom.
OL,10,FLocal MP David Mundell who served as
OL,11,FScottish Secretary from 2015 to 2019
OL,12,Fsaid: "Alex was one of the dominant
OL,13,Fpolitical figures of the last few
OL,14,Fdecades. He has dominated Scottish
OL,15,Fpolitics. He took independence right
OL,16,Fto the point of the referendum.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
