OL,3,CBorder politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'friend and inspiration' Alex Salmond
OL,6,F"I never found him an easy person to
OL,7,Fdeal with. He was very driven by his
OL,8,Fdesire for independence and obviously
OL,9,FI am, and many other people, are
OL,10,Fopposed that. We were political
OL,11,Fopponents, but he was formidable, and
OL,12,FI always respected that. He had
OL,13,Ftremendous political acumen."
OL,15,FJoan McAlpine, who is a former MSP and
OL,16,Fwho worked with Mr Salmond told ITV
OL,17,FBorder: "I'm devastated. I considered
OL,18,Fhim a friend as well as a political
OL,19,Fcolleague and indeed an inspiration.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
