OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F352A1728952370
OL,3,CBorder politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'friend and inspiration' Alex Salmond
OL,6,F"I saw him quite recently and he was
OL,7,Fthe same old Alex. Very cheerful,
OL,8,Fstill full of plans and schemes for
OL,9,Fthe future. It's just heartbreaking.
OL,10,FIt's a huge loss to Scotland."
OL,12,FMSP for the Scottish Borders,
OL,13,FChristine Grahame, added her
OL,14,Fcondolences saying: "Every political
OL,15,Fmovement needs a charismatic leader
OL,16,Fhead and shoulders above everybody
OL,17,Felse who also has a vision, the drive
OL,18,Fand a clever strategy. That's what he
OL,19,Fwas for the Scottish National Party
OL,20,Fand more particularly for the cause of
OL,21,Findependence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
