OL,3,CBorder politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'friend and inspiration' Alex Salmond
OL,6,F"Scotland owes much to this incredible
OL,7,Fstatesman and the independence cause
OL,8,Fand I personally, for his support as a
OL,9,Fcandidate, learning how to campaign
OL,10,Fand for listening to me, as a
OL,11,Fbackbencher even if he disagreed with
OL,12,Fmy point of view."
OL,14,FFollowing Mr Salmond's death, the
OL,15,FFirst Minister of Scotland, John
OL,16,FSwinney, reacted to the news.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
