OL,6,FHe said: "This is desperately sad news
OL,7,Fand I extend my deepest condolences to
OL,8,Fhis wife Moira, and to his family.
OL,9,FThis is a moment that individuals will
OL,10,Freflect on the exceptional leadership
OL,11,Fand contribution that Alex Salmond has
OL,12,Fgiven to public life in Scotland, with
OL,13,Fhis service in the House of Commons
OL,14,Fand in the Scottish Parliament, and
OL,15,Fespecially as the First Minister of
OL,16,FScotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
