OL,3,CBorder politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'friend and inspiration' Alex Salmond
OL,6,F"He took the SNP from the fringes of
OL,7,FScottish politics to become the
OL,8,Fgovernment of Scotland, and it took
OL,9,FScotland incredibly close to becoming
OL,10,Findependent. He has had a huge
OL,11,Fcontribution to the public life of
OL,12,FScotland over his life."
